.TH "dev_uc_add" 9 "dev_uc_add" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
dev_uc_add \- Add a secondary unicast address
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" dev_uc_add
.BI "(struct net_device *dev "  ","
.BI "const unsigned char *addr "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "dev" 12
device
.IP "addr" 12
address to add

Add a secondary unicast address to the device or increase
the reference count if it already exists.
